description: '''Sky Eats Airplane''' was an American [[electronicore]]/[[post-hardcore]] band from [[Fort worth, Texas]]. The band was signed to indie label [[Equal Vision Records]] and most recently released their self-titled full-length album through the label in July 2008. In March 2012, the official Sky Eats Airplane [[Facebook]] fan page indicated that there would be new SEA music sometime that year, although in November it was revealed that the band appears to be in an indefinite hiatus.
